2a16bdd0b56093af52c5","tid":1111953,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e33d33038537eb4c266d3cc30c3b0a77bbf4ce7","tid":1111953,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔係語言主導喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:07:27.000Z","msg":"快 想長知識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:23:02.000Z","msg":"有無試過想講一個字但諗唔起個term？<br />\n咁唔代表你諗唔起個concept<br />\n只係你腦內呢個concept同個名嘅mapping斷開咗<br />\n咁即係思想可以唔係語言主導<br />\n<br />\n舉多個例<br />\n你見到一樣物間<br />\n個腦第一時間會有相關聯想<br />\n例如有無危險，氣味，顏色，之前有無見過等等嘅感覺<br />\n但你唔會每見到一樣嘢個腦都講一次佢個名<br />\n車，師奶，街燈，紅燈，人，狗，人，阿叔，班馬線<br />\n否則你個腦都幾嘈"},{"pid":"d8e3daba443b72d09a70b8ad6149212f0c00395a","tid":1111953,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但簡單logic 有野要Process就唔係visualize 啦</blockquote>之前我都有過個po討論聾人點諗野<br />\n好似話佢地可以用visulize思考logic</blockquote>有分別掛 聾無左音 但仲有文字理解應用</blockquote>你嘅意思係佢地未學語言之前點<span style=\"color: red;\">諗</span>野?<br />\n根據以下個source 6-9 months已經可以意會一些日常用的句子，9估當時佢地未知乜撚野叫logical thinking住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.parentingheadline.com/index.php/zh/%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7/6044-%E3%80%90%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E3%80%91bb%E5%B9%BE%E6%99%82%E5%85%88%E8%AD%98%E8%AC%9B%E9%87%8E%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.parentingheadline.com%2Findex.php%2Fzh%2F%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%2F%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2595%25B7%2F6044-%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2595%25B7%25E3%2580%2591bb%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2585%2588%25E8%25AD%2598%25E8%25AC%259B%25E9%2587%258E%25EF%25BC%259F&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKOL6